so that they  read and find out what is wrong

02:32:34.719 --> 02:32:38.758
and what we have to do

02:32:59.133 --> 02:33:02.799
In the preface I have written

02:33:04.029 --> 02:33:08.500
Actually I did not want to write a book of this kind.

02:33:08.659 --> 02:33:12.823
I am a person who is in complete joy of Divinity.

02:33:13.095 --> 02:33:15.952
These is  all pervading joy of Divine love

02:33:16.217 --> 02:33:18.831
and I wanted everyone to enjoy it.

02:33:18.989 --> 02:33:23.388
Specially in the West I saw there are many seekers of Truth.

02:33:23.439 --> 02:33:28.949
There are many scientists who have written voluminous books about consciousness, about awareness.

02:33:29.056 --> 02:33:31.326
One can give a list of them.

02:33:31.517 --> 02:33:34.521
But all these books really weary you completely,

02:33:34.577 --> 02:33:37.787
because they do not emit any knowledge of the ultimate truth.

02:33:37.978 --> 02:33:40.544
I don’t want to criticise them;

02:33:40.632 --> 02:33:47.294
after all whatever they are doing constitutes honest research.

02:33:51.453 --> 02:33:56.659
But why not also give a chance to this new discovery which is being made?

02:33:56.762 --> 02:34:03.813
Why not humble down to see what is beyond
this mind which gives you all this artificial intelligence?

02:34:13.260 --> 02:34:17.615
It is extremely difficult for me to write about the problems of Western life.

02:34:17.703 --> 02:34:20.334
It is like a tree which has grown outside.

02:34:20.414 --> 02:34:25.418
This is how to be pushed down now to the roots and made to grow inside.

02:34:25.497 --> 02:34:32.232
It is only by going deep inside that we can find out
what the problems of Western civilisation are

02:34:32.377 --> 02:34:35.136
This book is especially meant for the Western people

02:34:35.256 --> 02:34:39.430
But  unfortunately I have never studied any Western language before.

02:34:40.458 --> 02:34:46.050
English is one of the blessings of the British given to India when they ruled our country.

02:34:46.130 --> 02:34:51.753
But there too, unfortunately, I studied in a vernacular school and later on in a medical college

02:34:51.849 --> 02:34:54.566
where there was no question of learning this language,

02:34:54.701 --> 02:35:00.689
English, which is today universally accepted, especially in the West,

02:35:02.768 --> 02:35:05.529
especially in the West.

02:35:06.966 --> 02:35:12.776
This book is no way to show any flowery language or to show any literary talent of mine.

02:35:12.895 --> 02:35:16.629
It is just a straightforward statement of facts which I know and

02:35:16.734 --> 02:35:19.816
which I want to communicate with the Western world.

02:35:19.960 --> 02:35:25.525
I would request people not to waste their time in finding faults with my English

02:35:25.614 --> 02:35:28.873
because that  is not my Mother tongue and I never studied it.

02:35:29.000 --> 02:35:35.901
Unfortunately, I could not get anybody else to write for me
because it had to be written by me personally.

02:35:36.118 --> 02:35:41.932
The most difficult part is to convince a human being that in the entire creation,

02:35:42.024 --> 02:35:44.005
he is the most highly evolved being;

02:35:44.108 --> 02:35:49.711
that he is capable of becoming a glorious personality,
a beautiful, peaceful angel.

02:35:49.839 --> 02:35:52.539
To tell him about the problems of modern times

02:35:52.610 --> 02:36:00.578
is not a very good way of convincing him
about what human beings truly are.

02:36:01.413 --> 02:36:04.769
There has been so much demeaning of human beings,

02:36:04.825 --> 02:36:07.438
so much of degradation in their value system

02:36:07.518 --> 02:36:11.147
that I thought that unless I go to the root of the problems,

02:36:11.249 --> 02:36:18.302
it won’t be easy to explain why they should
break away from their present shackles

02:36:19.465 --> 02:36:21.560
in order to evolve and ascend.

02:36:21.682 --> 02:36:26.788
One has to speak frankly what the problems
are and what the real solutions are.

02:36:28.039 --> 02:36:31.874
Frankly, there is no peace within modern human beings nor without.

02:36:32.026 --> 02:36:34.504
The poor and the rich alike are unhappy.

02:36:34.579 --> 02:36:37.255
Everywhere people are groping for solutions.

02:36:37.383 --> 02:36:46.419
At artifical  level, the intellect can work out certain
problems about things that we see around us in jeopardy.

02:36:46.721 --> 02:36:51.266
But while a few problems may be resolved in this way, others arise.

02:36:51.507 --> 02:36:55.789
The true solution lies not in the material circumstances outside

02:36:56.022 --> 02:36:59.633
human beings but inside the human beings

02:37:03.039 --> 02:37:05.342
inside the human beings themselves.

02:37:05.406 --> 02:37:11.445
True and lasting solution to present ills can be found only

02:37:11.794 --> 02:37:16.127
by inner, collective transformation of human beings.

02:37:16.375 --> 02:37:18.085
This is not an impossibility.

02:37:18.157 --> 02:37:20.434
In fact it has already happened.

02:37:20.529 --> 02:37:23.483
There are so many thousands and thousands...

02:37:23.658 --> 02:37:26.848
There are so many thousands and thousands

02:37:26.888 --> 02:37:29.688
who have actually achieved this state.

02:37:30.319 --> 02:37:34.015
The reality of en-masse inner ‘transformation of human beings

02:37:34.056 --> 02:37:39.444
by self-realisation is the most revolutionary discovery of the present age.

02:37:39.606 --> 02:37:43.708
But so far, very few governments have accepted this discovery,

02:37:43.797 --> 02:37:53.303
especially in America, England, France, Italy and Germany.

02:37:53.414 --> 02:37:58.276
The Pope, who himself is supposed to be in charge of religion,
meets all false gurus,

02:37:58.356 --> 02:38:00.895
but he will never meet me or talk to me,

02:38:00.988 --> 02:38:05.204
though I have met him before he was elected to this position of a Pope.

02:38:05.297 --> 02:38:08.072
This is not my job, this is not my work,

02:38:08.170 --> 02:38:14.119
but it is a spontaneous desire of the Divine
that this should be brought in full light,

02:38:14.526 --> 02:38:20.020
in full light, so that human beings are raised to a higher state of consciousness

02:38:20.076 --> 02:38:22.107
by which they can realise

02:38:22.186 --> 02:38:27.019
what they are, so that they can appreciate and glorify themselves.

02:38:27.207 --> 02:38:31.407
To me,  human beings are like the deities who are still in stone form

02:38:31.582 --> 02:38:35.467
and who can be transformed, with Kundalini awakening, into angels.

02:38:35.587 --> 02:38:38.384
I wish  with this book I will not hurt people.

02:38:38.544 --> 02:38:44.286
On the contrary, I hope to be able to get many
more people in this great work of Sahaja Yoga,

02:38:44.350 --> 02:38:46.598
by which they can achieve the ultimate.

02:38:46.678 --> 02:38:50.515
I have to use humour, because by nature I am very humourous

02:38:50.611 --> 02:38:56.671
and I see humour in every kind of incident,
which people sometimes take very seriously.

02:38:56.850 --> 02:39:00.326
It is too much for a Mother to talk about the ills of her children,

02:39:00.497 --> 02:39:05.515
but unless and until that is faced, I don’t think the children can ever get

02:39:06.182 --> 02:39:11.363
their benevolence and reach the ultimate goal, which is their self-realisation.

02:39:11.538 --> 02:39:14.749
So I would ask all of you not to get angry with me,

02:39:14.789 --> 02:39:18.649
but to understand that out of my tremendous compassion and love,

02:39:18.769 --> 02:39:21.945
I have written this book for the benevolence of the people,

02:39:22.001 --> 02:39:28.260
with whatever English I can use, with whatever literature I can use,
with whatever style I could adopt.
